modName: Hale - Elisif the Fair - Emphasis on Fair
summary: Facial overhaul of the Solitude Jarl. Complete with necessary FaceGen files.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/0epQl2O.png[/img]

Facial overhaul of the Solitude Jarl. Complete with necessary FaceGen files. Made with Enhanced Character Edit & the Creation Kit.

Complement with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30823]Iridum Eyes[/url] and Nuska's Textures (available in the resource pack) or SG Textures. I use customized Nuska Textures.

Extract to Data folder, or install through NMM.[/center]
author: Halendia
